                              <VBox>
                                 <children>
                                    <Label text="Blue Conveyer Belts">
                                       <font>
                                          <Font name="System Bold" size="12.0" />
                                       </font>
                                       <VBox.margin>
                                          <Insets top="5.0" />
                                       </VBox.margin>
                                    </Label>
                                    <Label text="Blue conveyor belts move any robot resting on them two spaces &#10;in the direction of the arrows.">
                                       <VBox.margin>
                                          <Insets top="20.0" />
                                       </VBox.margin>
                                    </Label>
                                    <Label text="Green Conveyer Belts">
                                       <VBox.margin>
                                          <Insets top="35.0" />
                                       </VBox.margin>
                                       <font>
                                          <Font name="System Bold" size="12.0" />
                                       </font>
                                    </Label>
                                    <Label text="Green conveyor belts move any robot resting on them one space &#10;in the direction of the arrows.">
                                       <VBox.margin>
                                          <Insets top="20.0" />
                                       </VBox.margin>
                                    </Label>
                                    <Label text="Push Panels">
                                       <VBox.margin>
                                          <Insets top="40.0" />
                                       </VBox.margin>
                                       <font>
                                          <Font name="System Bold" size="12.0" />
                                       </font>
                                    </Label>
                                    <Label text="Push panels push any robot resting on them into the next space in the direction the push panel faces. &#10;The panels activate only in the register that corresponds to the number on them. ">
                                       <VBox.margin>
                                          <Insets top="10.0" />
                                       </VBox.margin>
                                    </Label>
                                    <Label text="Gears">
                                       <VBox.margin>
                                          <Insets top="65.0" />
                                       </VBox.margin>
                                       <font>
                                          <Font name="System Bold" size="12.0" />
                                       </font>
                                    </Label>
                                    <Label text="Gears rotate robots resting on them 90 degrees &#10;in the direction of the arrows.">
                                       <VBox.margin>
                                          <Insets top="10.0" />
                                       </VBox.margin>
                                    </Label>
                                    <Label text="Board Lasers">
                                       <VBox.margin>
                                          <Insets top="40.0" />
                                       </VBox.margin>
                                       <font>
                                          <Font name="System Bold" size="12.0" />
                                       </font>
                                    </Label>
                                    <Label text="Board Lasers fire, hitting any robots in their line of sight. &#10;Board lasers cannot fire through walls, the priority antenna, or hit more than one robot, &#10;and they shoot from the red and white pointer. (Take a Spam damage card for each laser that hits you.">
                                       <VBox.margin>
                                          <Insets top="10.0" />
                                       </VBox.margin>
                                    </Label>
                                    <Label text="Energy Spaces">
                                       <VBox.margin>
                                          <Insets top="40.0" />
                                       </VBox.margin>
                                       <font>
                                          <Font name="System Bold" size="12.0" />
                                       </font>
                                    </Label>
                                    <Label text="When you end a register on an energy space, if there is an energy cube there, take it. &#10;If you end the fifth register on an energy space, take an energy cube from the energy bank.">
                                       <VBox.margin>
                                          <Insets top="10.0" />
                                       </VBox.margin>
                                    </Label>
                                    <Label text="Checkpoints">
                                       <VBox.margin>
                                          <Insets top="40.0" />
                                       </VBox.margin>
                                       <font>
                                          <Font name="System Bold" size="12.0" />
                                       </font>
                                    </Label>
                                    <Label text="You must reach checkpoints in numerical order. In order to reach a checkpoint, you must be on it &#10;at the end of a register and you may enter a checkpoint from any side. &#10;After you reach a checkpoint, take a checkpoint token, and place it on your player mat &#10;to track your progress in the race.&#10;">
                                       <VBox.margin>
                                          <Insets top="5.0" />
                                       </VBox.margin>
                                    </Label>
                                    <Label text="Rotating Conveyer Belts">
                                       <VBox.margin>
                                          <Insets top="35.0" />
                                       </VBox.margin>
                                       <font>
                                          <Font name="System Bold" size="12.0" />
                                       </font>
                                    </Label>
                                    <Label text="Robots rotate 90 degrees in the direction of the curved arrow &#10;as they move onto the curved section of the belt.">
                                       <VBox.margin>
                                          <Insets top="10.0" />
                                       </VBox.margin>
                                    </Label>
                                    <Label text="Pits">
                                       <VBox.margin>
                                          <Insets top="35.0" />
                                       </VBox.margin>
                                       <font>
                                          <Font name="System Bold" size="12.0" />
                                       </font>
                                    </Label>
                                    <Label text="If you land on a pit, &#10;you immediately fall in and must reboot your robot.">
                                       <VBox.margin>
                                          <Insets top="10.0" />
                                       </VBox.margin>
                                    </Label>
                                    <Label text="Walls">
                                       <VBox.margin>
                                          <Insets top="50.0" />
                                       </VBox.margin>
                                       <font>
                                          <Font name="System Bold" size="12.0" />
                                       </font>
                                    </Label>
                                    <Label text="Robots cannot move through walls, &#10;and robot and board lasers cannot shoot through walls">
                                       <VBox.margin>
                                          <Insets top="10.0" />
                                       </VBox.margin>
                                    </Label>
                                    <Label text="Priority Antenna">
                                       <VBox.margin>
                                          <Insets top="50.0" />
                                       </VBox.margin>
                                       <font>
                                          <Font name="System Bold" size="12.0" />
                                       </font>
                                    </Label>
                                    <Label text="The priority antenna helps determine whose turn it is. &#10;As a board element, it acts as a wall. Robots cannot move through, push, shoot through, &#10;or occupy the same space as the priority antenna. ">
                                       <VBox.margin>
                                          <Insets top="10.0" />
                                       </VBox.margin>
                                    </Label>
                                    <Label text="Reboot">
                                       <VBox.margin>
                                          <Insets top="40.0" />
                                       </VBox.margin>
                                       <font>
                                          <Font name="System Bold" size="12.0" />
                                       </font>
                                    </Label>
                                    <Label text="When you fall off the board or into a pit, or when you activate a worm card, &#10;you must reboot your robot.">
                                       <VBox.margin>
                                          <Insets top="10.0" />
                                       </VBox.margin>
                                    </Label>
